<H1>Remember the Cadet</H1>

</CENTER>

<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<FONT SIZE="+1">
<FONT SIZE="+3">A</FONT> cadet is the <B>most</B> important person.<BR>
<FONT SIZE="+3">A</FONT> cadet is not dependant on us - we are dependant on them.<BR>
<FONT SIZE="+3">A</FONT> cadet is not an interruption to our work - they are the purpose for it.<BR>
<FONT SIZE="+3">A</FONT> cadet is part of our business - not an outsider. They are human beings with feelings and deserve to be treated with respect.<BR>
<FONT SIZE="+3">A</FONT> cadet is a person who comes to us with their needs and wants - it is our job to fill them.<BR>
<FONT SIZE="+3">A</FONT> cadet deserves the most courteous attention we can give them. They are the life blood of this organisation. We would have to close our doors without them!<BR>
</FONT>
